<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.4">
<l>kallār matiḷcūḻ kacci nakaruḷ naccip pāṭakattuḷ</l>
<l>ellā vulakum vaṇaṅka virunta vammā ṉilaṅkaikkōṉ</l>
<l>vallā ḷākam villāl muṉinta ventai vipīṭaṇaṟku</l>
<l>nallā ṉuṭaiya nāmañ collil namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say the name of the lord who sits in Pāṭakam [Temple],</l>
<l rend="indent">as all the world worships,</l>
<l>Happily in the city of Kacci, enclosed by stone-filled walls,</l>
<l>Our father who raged with a bow at the chest of the strong man, Laṅkā’s king,</l>
<l>The one who was virtuous to Vibhīśaṇa, [that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
